#!/bin/bash

set -e
set -x

VM_ID=$1
VM_NAME=$2
VM_TAGS=$3
VM_USER=$4
VM_PASSWORD=$5
VM_DOMAIN=$6
VM_SSH_KEYS=$7
VM_IMAGE=$8

qm unlock $VM_ID || true
qm destroy $VM_ID || true
qm create $VM_ID \
    --name $VM_NAME \
    --tags $VM_TAGS \
    --memory 4096 \
    --cores 2 \
    --net0 virtio,bridge=vmbr1 \
    --scsihw virtio-scsi-pci \
    --ciuser $VM_USER \
    --cipassword $VM_PASSWORD \
    --searchdomain $VM_DOMAIN \
    --sshkeys $VM_SSH_KEYS \
    --ipconfig0 ip=dhcp \
    --ostype l26 \
    --agent 1
virt-customize -a $VM_IMAGE --install qemu-guest-agent
qm set $VM_ID --scsi0 vmdata:0,import-from=$VM_IMAGE --boot order=scsi0 --ide2 vmdata:cloudinit
qm resize $VM_ID scsi0 8G
qm template $VM_ID

---
# Create Cloud-Init VM templates
# https://pve.proxmox.com/wiki/Cloud-Init_Support

# Install libguestfs
# https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/modules/apt_module.html
- name: "Install libguestfs"
  apt:
    name: ["libguestfs-tools"]
    state: latest
    update_cache: yes
    cache_valid_time: 3600

# https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/modules/file_module.html
- name: "Create Cloud Init directory"
  file:
    path: "{{ item }}"
    state: directory
    mode: "ugo+rwx"
    owner: nobody
    group: users
    recurse: true
  with_items:
    - "{{ cloud_init_dir }}"

  # https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/collections/ansible/builtin/command_module.html
- name: "Rescan images"
  ansible.builtin.command: "qm rescan"

# https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/playbook_guide/playbooks_blocks.html
- name: "Create Cloud-Init VM templates"
  block:
    # Download cloud images
    # https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/collections/ansible/builtin/get_url_module.html
    - name: "Download cloud images"
      # Re-create the images when the downloaded image changed
      register: download
      get_url:
        url: "{{ item.url }}"
        dest: "{{ item.file }}"
        mode: "ugo+rwx"
        owner: nobody
        group: users
        timeout: 120
      with_items: "{{ images }}"

    # Destroy the image if it exists
    - name: "Get image config"
      register: config
      ansible.builtin.command: "qm config {{ item.id }}"
      ignore_errors: true
      with_items: "{{ images }}"
    - name: "Destroy image"
      ansible.builtin.command: "qm destroy {{ item.item.id }} --destroy-unreferenced-disks 1 --skiplock 1"
      when: item.rc == 0 # && download.changed
      with_items: "{{ config.results }}"

    - name: "Create image"
      # when: download.changed
      ansible.builtin.command:
        argv:
          - "qm"
          - "create"
          - "{{ item.id }}"
          - "--name"
          - "{{ item.name }}"
          - "--tags"
          - "{{ item.tags }}"
          - "--memory"
          - "4096"
          - "--cores"
          - "2"
          - "--net0"
          - "virtio,bridge=vmbr1"
          - "--scsihw"
          - "virtio-scsi-pci"
          - "--ciuser"
          - "{{ cloud_init_user }}"
          - "--cipassword"
          - "{{ cloud_init_password }}"
          - "--searchdomain"
          - "{{ cloud_init_domain }}"
          - "--sshkeys"
          - "{{ cloud_init_ssh_keys }}"
          - "--ipconfig0"
          - "ip=dhcp"
          - "--ostype"
          - "l26"
          - "--agent"
          - "1"
      with_items: "{{ images }}"

    - name: "Customize disk image"
      # when: download.changed
      ansible.builtin.command: "virt-customize -a {{ item.image }} --install qemu-guest-agent"
      with_items: "{{ images }}"

    - name: "Add disk image"
      # when: download.changed
      ansible.builtin.command: "qm set {{ item.id }} --scsi0 vmdata:0,import-from={{ item.file }} --boot order=scsi0 --ide2 vmdata:cloudinit"
      with_items: "{{ images }}"

    - name: "Resize disk image"
      # when: download.changed
      ansible.builtin.command: "qm resize {{ item.id }} scsi0 8G"
      with_items: "{{ images }}"

    - name: "Convert to template"
      # when: download.changed
      ansible.builtin.command: "qm template {{ item.id }}"
      with_items: "{{ images }}"

  vars:
    images:
      - {
          id: "9001",
          name: "ubuntu-jammy-template",
          tags: "ubuntu,jammy,cloud-image",
          file: "{{ cloud_init_dir }}/jammy-server-cloudimg-amd64.img",
          url: "https://cloud-images.ubuntu.com/jammy/current/jammy-server-cloudimg-amd64.img",
        }
      - {
          id: "9002",
          name: "debian-bookworm-template",
          tags: "debian,bookworm,cloud-image",
          file: "{{ cloud_init_dir }}/debian-12-genericcloud-amd64.qcow2",
          url: "https://cloud.debian.org/images/cloud/bookworm/latest/debian-12-genericcloud-amd64.qcow2",
        }

''' https://t.me/dev_survival '''

import configparser
from typing import Any
from dataclasses import dataclass

@dataclass
class LoggerConfig:
    version: int = 1
    use_cache: bool = True
    console_colors: bool = True
    root_propagate: bool = True
    disable_existing_loggers: bool = False
    timestamper: str = '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'
    file_level: str = 'DEBUG'
    console_level: str = 'DEBUG'
    root_level: str = 'DEBUG'
    file_log: str = 'logs/application.log'

@dataclass
class Config:
    logger: LoggerConfig

@dataclass
class ConfigStruct:
    section: str
    option: str

class Configuration:
    def __init__(self, path: str):
        self.config = configparser.ConfigParser()
        self.config.read(path)

    def getValue(self, _type: Any, _section, _option, _default: Any) -> Any:
        if _type is int: value = self.config.getint(_section, _option)
        elif _type is float: value = self.config.getint(_section, _option)
        elif _type is bool: value = self.config.getboolean(_section, _option)
        elif _type is list: value = list(map(Any, self.config.get(_section, _option).split(",")))
        else: value = self.config.get(_section, _option)

        if value is not None: return value
        return _default


    def load(self) -> Config:
        return Config(
            logger = LoggerConfig(
                version = self.getValue(int, 'LoggerConfig', 'version', LoggerConfig.version),
                use_cache = self.getValue(bool, 'LoggerConfig', 'use_cache', LoggerConfig.use_cache),
                console_colors = self.getValue(bool, 'LoggerConfig', 'console_colors', LoggerConfig.console_colors),
                root_propagate = self.getValue(bool, 'LoggerConfig', 'root_propagate', LoggerConfig.root_propagate),
                disable_existing_loggers = self.getValue(bool, 'LoggerConfig', 'disable_existing_loggers', LoggerConfig.disable_existing_loggers),
                timestamper = self.getValue(str, 'LoggerConfig', 'timestamper', LoggerConfig.timestamper),
                file_level = self.getValue(str, 'LoggerConfig', 'file_level', LoggerConfig.file_level),
                console_level = self.getValue(str, 'LoggerConfig', 'console_level', LoggerConfig.console_level),
                root_level = self.getValue(str, 'LoggerConfig', 'root_level', LoggerConfig.root_level),
                file_log = self.getValue(str, 'LoggerConfig', 'file_log', LoggerConfig.file_log),
            )
        )





if __name__ == '__main__':
    configuration = Configuration(path='config.ini')
    config = configuration.load()

    print(config)
    print(type(config.logger.console_colors))
    '''
    Output:
        Config(
            logger = LoggerConfig(
                version=1,
                use_cache=True,
                console_colors=True,
                root_propagate=True,
                disable_existing_loggers=False,
                timestamper='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S',
                file_level='DEBUG',
                console_level='DEBUG',
                root_level='DEBUG',
                file_log='logs/application.log'
        ))
    '''

import json
from http.server import BaseHTTPRequestHandler, HTTPServer
from shapely.geometry import Point, Polygon

class StateHandler(BaseHTTPRequestHandler):

    def load_states_data(self, file_path):

        with open(file_path) as f:
            states_data = json.load(f)

        return states_data
    

    def determine_state(self, latitude, longitude, states_data):

        point = Point(longitude, latitude)

        state = None

        for state in states_data:

            borders = state['border']
            state_border_polygon = Polygon(borders)

            if state_border_polygon.contains(point):
                state = state['state']

                break

        return state
    
    def do_POST(self):
        
        content_length = int(self.headers['Content-Length'])
        post_data = self.rfile.read(content_length)
        data = post_data.decode('utf-8')

        location_strings = data.split('&')

        for string in location_strings:
            key, value = string.split('=')

            if key == 'latitude':
                latitude = float(value)

            if key == 'longitude':
                longitude = float(value)
        
        
        states_data = self.load_states_data('states2.json')

        state = self.determine_state(latitude, longitude, states_data)

        self.send_response(200)
        self.send_header('Content-type', 'application/json')
        self.end_headers()

        if state:
            response = json.dumps({'state': state})
            self.wfile.write(response.encode('utf-8'))
        else:
            response = json.dumps({'error': 'Point is not within any state boundary'})
            self.wfile.write(response.encode('utf-8'))


def run_server(server_class=HTTPServer, handler_class=StateHandler, port=8080):
    server_address = ('', port)
    httpd = server_class(server_address, handler_class)
    print('Server running on port', port)
    httpd.serve_forever()

if __name__ == "__main__":
    run_server()

title: Ivan explanation controllers and routes in python
content:
# controller
## users_controllers.py

def query_all_users():
    return db.get.users


def format_users():
    users = query_all_users()
    if users >= 0:
        return json.dumps({"users": users}), 200

    return json.dumps({"message": "failed fetching users"}), 500

# routes
## user_routes
@endpoint("/something", "GET")
def get_users_route(req):
    # pass req if you need to work with any info provided from the request
    return format_users(req) # you can call this one get_users_controller if you wish


# how to test
def test_format_users__users_are_present():
    users = [{}, {}, {}]
    mock("query_all_users", users)
    _, status_code = format_users()

    assert status_code == 200

def test_format_users__users_do_not_exist():
    users = None
    mock("query_all_users", users)
    _, status_code = format_users()

    assert status_code == 500

# find_nearest.py

import math

def levenshtein_distance(s1, s2):
    if len(s1) < len(s2):
        return levenshtein_distance(s2, s1)

    # len(s1) >= len(s2)
    if len(s2) == 0:
        return len(s1)

    # create two lists a and b for current and previous row
    a = list(range(len(s2) + 1))
    b = [0] * (len(s2) + 1)

    for i, c1 in enumerate(s1):
        b[0] = i + 1
        for j, c2 in enumerate(s2):
            cost = 0 if c1 == c2 else 1
            b[j + 1] = min(b[j] + 1, a[j + 1] + 1, a[j] + cost)
        a, b = b, a

    return a[-1]

def predict(test_set, training_set):
    predicted = len(test_set)
    for x1 in test_set:
        distance_from_x1 = []
        for x2 in training_set:
            distance = levenshtein_distance(x1, x2)
            distance_from_x1.append((distance, x2))
        sorted_distances = sorted(distance_from_x1)
        
        guess = sorted_distances[0][1]
        
        print(f"\nAltered Test: {x1}")
        match_percentage = round((1 - sorted_distances[0][0] / max(len(x1), len(guess))) * 100, 6)
        print(f"\tGuessing Nearest Match: {guess} at {match_percentage}%")
        if answers[x1] == guess:
            print("\t+++ CORRECT +++")
        else:
            print(f"\t\tExpected Answer: {answers[x1]}")
            predicted = predicted - 1
    print(f"\n\nPredicted: {predicted} out of {len(test_set)}")
	
# for testing
import random
import string

letters = list(string.ascii_letters)
L = len(letters)

tests = []
def generate_tests(num_tests):
	i = 0
	for _ in range(num_tests):
		test = ''
		for _ in range(25):
			s = letters.pop(i%11)
			letters.append(s)
			i += 1
			test += s
		tests.append(test)
		s = letters.pop(i%7)
		letters.append(s)

def alter_test(test):
	pos = random.sample(range(25), 12) # choose two positions to change
	new_test = list(test)
	new_test[pos[0]] = letters[(letters.index(new_test[pos[0]]) + random.randint(1, L - 1)) % L]
	new_test[pos[1]] = letters[(letters.index(new_test[pos[1]]) + random.randint(1, L - 1)) % L]
	return ''.join(new_test)

# generate a list of n random n-letter tests
generate_tests(1000)

# make a copy of each test with two letters changed
altered_tests = [alter_test(test) for test in tests]
answers = dict(zip(altered_tests, tests))
random.shuffle(tests)

# predict nearest matches for each altered test
predict(altered_tests, tests)

title: 88. Merge Sorted Array
content:
class Solution:
    def merge(self, nums1: List[int], m: int, nums2: List[int], n: int) -> None:
        """
        Do not return anything, modify nums1 in-place instead.
        """
        #TC: O(M + N)
        #SC: O(3) = O(1)

        # [1, 2, 2, 3, 5, 6]
        #  i/k       
        # [2, 5, 6]
        #j

        #Cách làm: sử dụng kĩ thuật two pointers, bắt đầu từ cuối 2 mảng nums1, nums2
        #So sánh nums1[i] và nums2[j], thằng nào lớn hơn thì dịch con trò của nó sang trái, và đưa vào nums1.
        #Đến khi một mảng đã hết rồi thì dừng, và dồn tất cả các phần tử của mảng còn lại vào nums1.

        #Two pointers
        i, j = m - 1, n - 1
        #Another pointer to insert merged numbers in
        k = m + n - 1

        #Khi vẫn còn phần tử ở cả 2 mảng
        while i >= 0 and j >= 0:
            #So sánh
            if nums1[i] >= nums2[j]:
                nums1[k] = nums1[i]
                #dịch con trỏ i sang trái
                i -= 1
            else:
                nums1[k] = nums2[j]
                #dịch con trỏ j sang trái
                j -= 1
            k -= 1
        
        while j >= 0:
            nums1[k] = nums2[j]
            j -= 1
            k -= 1

title: 303. Range Sum Query - Immutable
content:
class NumArray:

    # nums = [-2, 0, 3, -5, 2, -1]
    # pref = [0, -2, -2, 1, -4, -2, -3]
    # sum(nums[2:5]) = pref[5] - pref[2]

    def __init__(self, nums: List[int]):
        #TC: O(N)
        #SC: O(N)
        #prefix_sum[i] = tong cua nums tu 0 den i - 1
        #-->
        #prefix_sum[0] = 0
        #prefix_sum[i] = prefix_sum[i - 1] + nums[i]
        self.prefix_sum = [0]
        for num in nums:
            self.prefix_sum.append(self.prefix_sum[-1] + num)

    def sumRange_old(self, left: int, right: int) -> int:
        #TC: O(right - left)
        #SC: O(1)
        current_sum = 0
        for i in range(left, right + 1):
            current_sum += self.nums[i]
        return current_sum

    def sumRange(self, left: int, right: int) -> int:
        #TC: O(1)
        #SC: O(1)
        return self.prefix_sum[right + 1] - self.prefix_sum[left]
    
# Your NumArray object will be instantiated and called as such:
# obj = NumArray(nums)
# param_1 = obj.sumRange(left,right)

title: sqlparse error
content:
import re

import sqlparse
from sqllineage.core.models import Column
from sqllineage.core.parser.sqlparse.models import SqlParseColumn
from sqlparse.sql import (
    Token,
)
from copy import deepcopy

raw_query = """
create temp table autofaq_chats_creating_chats_1 as(
with
cte_autofaq_event_t1 AS (
        SELECT
            id AS item_id,
            conversation_id,
            to_timestamp((ts::float/ 1000)) AS item_time,
            tpe AS item_type,
            LEFT(txt, 5096) AS message_text,
            channel_message_id  AS channel_message_id,
            NULLIF(COALESCE(NULLIF(nullif(operator_id,''),'autoFAQ'), assigned_operator_id),'') AS full_operator_id,
            auto_faq_info AS autofaq_additional_info,
            message_score,
            document_id,
            service_id,
            service_name,
            payload AS event_additional_info,
            rate,
            rate_label,
            src,
            ts,
            event_tpe AS event_type,
            CASE WHEN event_tpe IN ('CreatedByOperator','CreatedByDelayedDelivery') THEN 1 ELSE 0 end as outcoming_flg,
            MIN(CASE WHEN NULLIF(COALESCE(NULLIF(nullif(operator_id,''),'autoFAQ'), assigned_operator_id),'') IS NULL
                THEN NULL ELSE ts END)
                OVER (PARTITION BY conversation_id order by ts ROWS BETWEEN CURRENT ROW and UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING) AS min_operator_time
        FROM "dm_stage_temp"."13903-201050-20230730T210000-raw" cm  -- raw_autofaq_1390.conversation_messages
        WHERE to_timestamp((ts/ 1000)) > '2021-01-01'
            and mt_actual_flag
        )


SELECT
    t1.*,
    MIN(rechat_time)
        OVER (PARTITION BY item_id) AS min_rechat_time
FROM cte_autofaq_event_t1 t1
left join (select conversation_id,ts as rechat_time from cte_autofaq_event_t1 where event_type in ('ReturnToQueue','CloseConversation','ChangeGroup')) rechat
    on t1.conversation_id = rechat.conversation_id
    and rechat_time >= min_operator_time
)
  DISTRIBUTED BY (conversation_id);

create temp table autofaq_chats_creating_chats_2 as(
with cte_operators AS (
    SELECT
        id AS operator_id,
        coalesce(    CASE 
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'ТП-%'))
            THEN 'ТП'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'ТП - %'))
            THEN 'ТП'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'КЦ -%'))
            THEN 'КЦ'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'КЦ-%'))
            THEN 'КЦ'
        WHEN ((full_nm like '%intTS%'))
            THEN 'ТП Int'
        WHEN ((full_nm like '%PremES%'))
            THEN 'Prem ES'
        WHEN ((full_nm like '%PremIT%'))
            THEN 'Prem IT'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'Schedule-%'))
            THEN 'Schedule'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'WA-%')) and ((settings_nm like '%[121774]%'))
            THEN 'Schedule'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'Исход-%'))
            THEN 'UTC'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'Outint-%'))
            THEN 'UTC Int'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'Teachers Care%FINANCE%'))
            THEN 'Teachers Care (finance)'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'Teachers Care-%'))
            THEN 'Teachers Care'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'Sales 1Л-%'))
            THEN 'Sales 1Л'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'Sales 1Л %'))
            THEN 'Sales 1Л'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'ТС-%'))
            THEN 'ТС'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'TC-%'))
            THEN 'ТС'
        WHEN ((full_nm like '%SC%'))
            THEN 'ТС'
        WHEN ((full_nm IN ('Валентина Замукова - TC', 'Олег Чернобривец-ТС')))
            THEN 'ТС'
        WHEN ((full_nm like '%ТПPrem%'))
            THEN 'ТПPrem'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'ТТС-%'))
            THEN 'TTC'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'ТТСkids%'))
            THEN 'TTC'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'ТТС kids%'))
            THEN 'TTC'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'X-%'))
            THEN 'Х'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'Х-'))
            THEN 'Х'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'МС-'))
            THEN 'Methodology Care'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'МР-'))
            THEN 'Methodology Premium'
        WHEN ((full_nm like 'SQ-'))
            THEN 'Вопросы по предмету'
        WHEN ((full_nm NOT like '%-%'))
            THEN 'other'
        WHEN ((full_nm IN ('mzavatsky - Разработка', 'teachers-methodology-kids-vimbot','bot_26_do_not_disable@skyeng.ru - НЕ ТРОГАТЬ!',
            '-Nikita Rakov','Настя Павлова (-28 test prod)','bot_11_do_not_disable@skyeng.ru - НЕ ТРОГАТЬ!','Настя Павлова (-28 тест КЦ)',
            'Евгений Галата - КЦ','bot_26_do_not_disable@skyeng.ru - НЕ ТРОГАТЬ!','bot_18_do_not_disable@skyeng.ru - НЕ ТРОГАТЬ!',
            'Евгений Галата - ТП')))
            THEN 'other'
        WHEN ((full_nm is null))
            THEN 'other'
        ELSE null
    END,split_part(full_name, '-', 1)) as operator_group_nm,
        login,
        full_name
    FROM (
        select
            *,
            full_name as full_nm,
            settings::text as settings_nm
        from raw_autofaq_1390.operator_autofaq
        where mt_actual_flag
        ) ao
    group by 1,2,3,4
),


cte_autofaq_event_t3 AS (
select
    distinct
    conversation_id,
    min_rechat_time,
    FIRST_VALUE(full_operator_id) OVER (PARTITION BY min_rechat_time ORDER BY TS) AS chat_operator_id,
    DENSE_RANK() OVER (partition by conversation_id ORDER BY min_rechat_time) AS chat_num

FROM autofaq_chats_creating_chats_1
WHERE full_operator_id IS NOT null
)


  select
        distinct
        item_id::text,
        t2.conversation_id::text as conversation_id,
        t2.item_time::timestamp,
        item_type::text,
        operator_group_nm::text,
        event_type::text,
        chat_operator_id::text as operator_id,
        login,
        rate,
        full_name AS operator_name,
        t2.conversation_id::text || '-' || COALESCE(chat_num,(coalesce(MAX(chat_num) over (partition by t2.conversation_id),0))+1)  as chat_id,
        event_additional_info,
        SUM(outcoming_flg) OVER (PARTITION BY t2.conversation_id)::float as is_outcoming,
        case when item_type = 'Question' or event_type = 'AssignToOperator' then
            MIN(case when item_type = 'AnswerOperator' then item_time::timestamp end)
            over (partition by conversation_id, chat_num order by ts rows between 1 following and unbounded FOLLOWING)
                end as next_operators_answer

    FROM autofaq_chats_creating_chats_1 t2
    left join cte_autofaq_event_t3 t3
        using(conversation_id, min_rechat_time)
    LEFT JOIN cte_operators op
        ON op.operator_id = chat_operator_id
  )
  DISTRIBUTED BY (chat_id);




INSERT INTO "dm_stage"."autofaq_chats" (
        autofaq_chat_pk,
        conversation_id,
        operator_group_nm,
        operator_id,
        login_nm,
        operator_nm,
        operator_first_message_dttm,
        student_first_question_dttm,
        last_event_dttm,
        first_event_dttm,
        is_bot,
        is_assigned,
        is_operator,
        is_outcoming,
        operator_messages_cnt,
        operator_messages_with_bot_cnt,
        chat_rate,
        assigned_dttm,
        status_nm,
        channel_id,
        tags_nm,
        education_service_fk,
        education_service_begin_dttm,
        sub_theme_id,
        chatbot_session_id,
        service_nm,
        channel_nm,
        time_for_answers_sec_amt,
        answers_cnt,
        mt_proc_id,
        mt_ins_dttm,
        mt_hash
)
    with
cte_conversation AS (
    select
        id as conversation_id,
        session_id,
        status as status_nm,
        TO_TIMESTAMP(ts_create::float / 1000) at time zone 'Europe/Moscow'   as ts_create,
        service_id,
        operator_user_id as last_operator,
        channel_user_id as user_id,
        channel_id,
        tags_nm,
        education_service_id,
        sub_theme_id,
        chatbot_session_id
    from raw_autofaq_1390.conversation
    where channel_id<>'1ed0f8af-4b1c-4b4c-91b4-b279af38b079' --чаты, создаваемые мониторингом
        and TO_TIMESTAMP(ts_create / 1000) > '2021-01-01'
        and mt_actual_flag
)


,art_calc_temp as (
select
    next_operators_answer,
    conversation_id,
    chat_id,
    coalesce(MAX(case when event_type = 'AssignToOperator' then item_time else null end), min(item_time))  as first_message_from_student
from autofaq_chats_creating_chats_2
where next_operators_answer is not null
group by 1, 2, 3

)

, art_calc as (
select
    conversation_id,
    chat_id,
    SUM(extract( epoch from next_operators_answer - first_message_from_student)) as time_for_answers,
    count(next_operators_answer) as cnt_answers
from art_calc_temp
group by 1, 2

)

,
cte_autofaq_event_t5 AS (
    SELECT
        conversation_id,
        operator_group_nm,
        chat_id as autofaq_chat_pk,
        operator_id,
        login as login_nm,
        operator_name as operator_nm,
        min(case when item_type ~ 'AnswerOperator' then item_time else null end) as operator_first_message_dttm,
        min(case when event_type ~ 'FirstTimeInQueue' or item_type = 'Question' then item_time else null end) as student_first_question_dttm,
        max(item_time) as last_event_dttm,
        min(item_time) as first_event_dttm,
        case
            when max(case when item_type = 'AnswerBot' then 1 else 0 end)  = 0 then FALSE
            else true
        end as is_bot,
        case
            when max(case when event_type = 'AssignToOperator' then 1 else 0 end)  = 0 then FALSE
            else true
        end as is_assigned,
        case
            when max(case when item_type ~ 'AnswerOperator' then 1 else 0 end)  = 0 then FALSE
            else true
        end as is_operator,
        case
            when MAX(is_outcoming) = 0 then FALSE
            else true
        end as is_outcoming,
        COUNT(case when item_type ~ 'AnswerOperator' then item_id else null end) as operator_messages_cnt,
        COUNT(case when item_type ~ 'AnswerOperatorWithBot' then item_id else null end) as operator_messages_with_bot_cnt,
        MIN(case when item_type ~ 'Rate' then rate end) as chat_rate,
        MIN(case when event_type = 'AssignToOperator' and event_additional_info::text ~ '"oid"' then item_time else null end) as assigned_dttm,
        avg(time_for_answers) as time_for_answers_sec,
        avg(cnt_answers) as answers_cnt
    FROM autofaq_chats_creating_chats_2
    left join art_calc
        using(chat_id, conversation_id)
    GROUP BY 1,2,3,4,5,6
)
SELECT
    ae.autofaq_chat_pk,
    ae.conversation_id,
    ae.operator_group_nm,
    ae.operator_id,
    ae.login_nm,
    ae.operator_nm,
    ae. operator_first_message_dttm,
    ae.student_first_question_dttm,
    ae.last_event_dttm,
    ae.first_event_dttm,
    ae.is_bot,
    ae.is_assigned,
    ae.is_operator,
    ae.is_outcoming,
    ae.operator_messages_cnt,
    ae.operator_messages_with_bot_cnt,
    max(ae.chat_rate) OVER (PARTITION BY ae.conversation_id) as chat_rate,
    ae.assigned_dttm,
    cn.status_nm,
    cn.channel_id,
    CASE
        WHEN length(cn.tags_nm) < 1 THEN NULL
        ELSE cn.tags_nm
    END AS tags_nm,
    cn.education_service_id as education_service_fk,
    es.begin_dttm as education_service_begin_dttm,
    cn.sub_theme_id,
    chatbot_session_id,
    sn.service_nm,
    coalesce(     CASE 
        WHEN ((channel_id = 'f93db590-68e5-4224-850b-3201a88e461d'))
            THEN 'Widget Skyeng'
        WHEN ((channel_id = '226c2fd7-cf8e-4b48-b308-b95733299165'))
            THEN 'Widget Skysmart'
        WHEN ((channel_id = '3e52032a-9ca6-474c-a1d9-0dd099515a16'))
            THEN 'Telegram Skysmart English'
        WHEN ((channel_id = 'fc8d787a-ac6f-4774-8113-8f87264326fe'))
            THEN 'Telegram Skyeng'
        WHEN ((channel_id = '6c020258-d3c5-4db7-9ef5-11c23a7c8770'))
            THEN 'WhatsApp CS CIS'
        WHEN ((channel_id = 'd1ae858b-54a4-4517-adbd-74117f430b44'))
            THEN 'Techsup acquisition'
        WHEN ((channel_id = '8db8b2ce-8efc-4514-b428-b8b6bcd68080'))
            THEN 'Telegram У ОШ'
        WHEN ((tpe_nm = 'Slack'))
            THEN 'Slack Support'
        WHEN ((tpe_nm = 'ExtApi'))
            THEN 'Vimbot'
        ELSE null
    END,p.name) AS channel_nm,
    time_for_answers_sec as time_for_answers_sec_amt,
    answers_cnt
FROM cte_autofaq_event_t5 ae
LEFT JOIN cte_conversation cn
    ON cn.conversation_id = ae.conversation_id
LEFT JOIN raw_mdm_mappings_380.q_service_names sn
    ON sn.service_id = cn.service_id
LEFT JOIN (
        select
            *,
            tpe as tpe_nm
        from raw_autofaq_1390.platforms
        where mt_actual_flag
        ) p
    ON p.id = cn.channel_id
left join cdm.education_service es
    on cn.education_service_id = es.education_service_pk
        and es.end_dttm = '2999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
"""


def linage():
    from sqllineage.runner import LineageRunner

    origin_of = deepcopy(SqlParseColumn.of)

    def of(column: Token, **kwargs) -> Column:
        print(column)
        return origin_of(column, **kwargs)

    SqlParseColumn.of = of

    REMOVE_BRACKETS_RE = re.compile(
        r"""(?P<ctas>CREATE (?:TEMP )?TABLE .*?(?:WITH\s*\(.*?\))?\s*AS\s*)\((?P<body>.*?)\)(?P<distribution>\s*DISTRIBUTED.*?)?\s*?;""",
        flags=re.IGNORECASE | re.MULTILINE | re.DOTALL)

    results = []

    queries = sqlparse.split(raw_query)
    for query in queries:
        if (match := re.search(REMOVE_BRACKETS_RE, query)) is None:
            clean_query = query
        else:
            clean_query = f"{match.group('ctas')} {match.group('body')} {match.group('distribution')};"
        results.append(sqlparse.format(clean_query))

    result = LineageRunner("\n\n".join(results), dialect="non-validating")
    print(result.target_tables)
    print(result.source_tables)


if __name__ == '__main__':
    linage()

local component = require("component")
local fs = require("filesystem")
local computer = require("computer")
local bridge = component.openperipheral_bridge
local gpu = component.gpu
local items = {
  {"IC2:itemIngot", 0},
  {"IC2:itemIngot", 1},
  {"minecraft:iron_ingot", 0},
  {"minecraft:gold_ingot", 0},
  {"minecraft:nether_star", 0},
  {"minecraft:diamond", 0},
  {"IC2:itemPlutonium", 0},
  {"IC2:itemRubber", 0}
}
 
local players = {
  {"_DeD_Makar_", false}
}
local chat_box, me, radar, counter
local average, me_a, cb, r = false, false, false, false
-------------{TIME OPTIONS}------------------
local TIME_ZONE = 2 --Ваш часовой пояс
---------------------------------------------
 
---------------------------------------------
local t_correction = TIME_ZONE * 3600
local chat_box_name = "§8[§4Алиса§8]"
local adm = "diza1" -- Ник админа компа
local allow_mem = true -- Отображать на экране кол-во памяти или нет
local localize = {
  time = "§9Время МСК:",
  join_in_game = " §7вошел в игру!",
  left_from_game = " §7покинул игру!",
  user_online = "online",
  user_offline = "offline",
  near_ME = "Игроки около МЭ"
}
local colors = {
  item_size = 0x05F5F0, -- кол-во предметов
  eu = 0x5555FF, -- еу/т
  mem = 0xFFFFFF, -- память
  time = 0x55F055, --Время
  time_text = 0x00FFFF, -- текст "Время МСК:"(пример)
  online = 0x008000, --оналайн на очках
  offline = 0xB22222, -- оффлайн на очках
  near = 0x0000CD, --текст "Игроки рядом с МЭ"
  players_near = 0xFF4500, -- цвет игроков рядом
  players = 0x228B22 -- цвет игроков в Online/offline
}
--------------------------------------------
 
function check()
  if component.isAvailable("average_counter") then
    average = true
    counter = component.average_counter
  end
  if component.isAvailable("chat_box") then
    cb = true
    chat_box = component.chat_box
    chat_box.setName(chat_box_name)
  end
  if component.isAvailable("me_controller") then
    me_a = true
    me = component.me_controller
  end
  if component.isAvailable("radar") then
    r = true
    radar = component.radar
  end
  componentsOnScreen()
end
 
local function getTimeHost()
  local file = io.open('/tmp/UNIX.tmp', 'w')
  file:write('TIME_ZONE = '..TIME_ZONE)
  file:close()
  local lastmod = tonumber(string.sub(fs.lastModified('/tmp/UNIX.tmp'), 1, -4)) + t_correction
  local dt = os.date('%H:%M:%S', lastmod)
  return dt
end
 
function addBox(x, y, w, h, color, tran)
  bridge.addBox(x, y, w, h, color, tran)
end
 
function addText(x, y, text, color)
  bridge.addText(x, y, text, color)
end
 
function addIcon(x, y, name, meta)
  bridge.addIcon(x, y, name, meta)
end
 
function gui()
  w, h = gpu.maxResolution()
  gpu.fill(1, 1, w, h, " ")
end
 
function componentsOnScreen()
  gpu.set(1, 1, "Chat-box: " .. tostring(cb))
  gpu.set(1, 2, "ME: " .. tostring(me_a))
  gpu.set(1, 3, "Radar: " .. tostring(r))
  gpu.set(1, 4, "Counter: " .. tostring(average))
end
 
function addAllIcons()
  y = 25
  for i = 1, #items do
    y = y + 15
    addIcon(0, y, items[i][1], items[i][2])
  end
end
 
function getSize(name,dmg)
 for _, item in ipairs(me.getItemsInNetwork()) do
  if item.name == name and item.damage == dmg then
   return item.size
  end
 end
 return 0
end
 
function setEnergy()
  addIcon(0, 25, "AdvancedSolarPanel:BlockMolecularTransformer", 0)
  if counter.getAverage() / 1000 <= 1 then
    av = string.format("%.3f", tostring(counter.getAverage())) .. "EU/t"
  elseif counter.getAverage() / 1000000 >= 1 then
    av = string.format("%.3f", tostring(counter.getAverage() / 1000000)) .. "MEU/t"
  else
    av = string.format("%.1f", tostring(counter.getAverage() / 1000)) .. "kEU/t"
  end
  addText(25, 27, av, colors.eu)
end
 
function setTime()
  addText(0, 2, localize.time, colors.time_text)
  addText(55, 2, getTimeHost(), colors.time)
end
 
function freeMemory()
  if allow_mem then
    addText(0, 12, "MEM: "..math.floor((computer.freeMemory() / 1000)).."mb".."/"..math.floor((computer.totalMemory() / 1000)).."mb".." "..math.floor(((computer.freeMemory() / computer.totalMemory()) * 100)).."%", colors.mem)
  end
end
 
function checkOnline(n)
  computer.removeUser(adm)
  if computer.addUser(players[n][1]) then
    computer.removeUser(players[n][1])
    if players[n][2] == false then
      if cb then
        chat_box.say("§a"..players[n][1] .. localize.join_in_game)
      end
      players[n][2] = true
    end
    return true
  else
    if players[n][2] == true then
      if cb then
        chat_box.say("§c"..players[n][1] .. localize.left_from_game)
      end
      players[n][2] = false
    end
    computer.removeUser(players[n][1])
    return false
  end
end
 
function drawOnline()
  yy = 17
  for i = 1, #players do
    yy = yy + 8
    addText(90, yy, players[i][1], colors.players)
    if checkOnline(i) then
      addText(130, yy, localize.user_online, colors.online)
    else
      addText(130, yy, localize.user_offline, colors.offline)
    end
  end
end
 
function getPlayersNearME()
  addText(90, 75, localize.near_ME, colors.near)
  a = 75
  temp = radar.getPlayers()
  for i = 1, #temp do
    a = a + 10
    for j = 1, #players do
      if temp[i].name == players[j][1] then
        return
      else
        addText(90, a, temp[i].name.." "..math.floor(temp[i].distance), colors.players_near)
      end
    end
  end
end
 
check()
bridge.clear()
addBox(25, 0, 100, 100, 0xFFFFFF, 0)
addAllIcons()
bridge.sync()
gui()
 
while true do
  check()
  computer.addUser(adm)
  bridge.clear()
  if me_a then
    addAllIcons()
    y = 27
    for i = 1, #items do
      y = y + 15
      addText(25, y, getSize(items[i][1], items[i][2]), colors.item_size)
    end
  end
  if average then
    setEnergy()
  end
  setTime()
  drawOnline()
  freeMemory()
  if r then
    getPlayersNearME()
  end
  os.sleep(0.001)
  bridge.sync()
end
